trans-unit.source: Represents a <xref href="System.Windows.Controls.DataGrid"></xref> column that hosts <xref href="System.Windows.Controls.CheckBox"></xref> controls in its cells.
trans-unit.target: Representa um <xref href="System.Windows.Controls.DataGrid"> </xref> coluna hospeda <xref href="System.Windows.Controls.CheckBox"> </xref> controles em suas células.

trans-unit.source: Use DataGridCheckBoxColumn to display columns of Boolean data as a <xref:System.Windows.Controls.CheckBox>.
trans-unit.target: Use DataGridCheckBoxColumn para exibir as colunas de dados Boolean como <xref:System.Windows.Controls.CheckBox>.</xref:System.Windows.Controls.CheckBox>

trans-unit.source: The following illustration shows an example of DataGridCheckBoxColumn.
trans-unit.target: A ilustração a seguir mostra um exemplo de DataGridCheckBoxColumn.

trans-unit.source: ![A DataGridCheckBox column](~/add/media/wpf-datagrid-checkbox.png "A DataGridCheckBox column") To populate the column, bind the column to the data by using the <xref:System.Windows.Controls.DataGridBoundColumn.Binding%2A> property.
trans-unit.target: ![Uma coluna DataGridCheckBox](~/add/media/wpf-datagrid-checkbox.png "DataGridCheckBox A coluna") para preencher a coluna, associe a coluna para os dados usando o <xref:System.Windows.Controls.DataGridBoundColumn.Binding%2A>propriedade.</xref:System.Windows.Controls.DataGridBoundColumn.Binding%2A>

trans-unit.source: The <xref:System.Windows.Controls.DataGridBoundColumn.Binding%2A> property is applied to the <xref:System.Windows.Controls.CheckBox> element created in the column.
trans-unit.target: O <xref:System.Windows.Controls.DataGridBoundColumn.Binding%2A>propriedade é aplicada para o <xref:System.Windows.Controls.CheckBox>elemento criado na coluna.</xref:System.Windows.Controls.CheckBox> </xref:System.Windows.Controls.DataGridBoundColumn.Binding%2A>

trans-unit.source: The <xref:System.Windows.FrameworkElement.DataContext%2A> for the element in each cell is the data item for the row the cell is in.
trans-unit.target: O <xref:System.Windows.FrameworkElement.DataContext%2A>elemento em cada célula é que o item de dados para a linha da célula é in.</xref:System.Windows.FrameworkElement.DataContext%2A>

trans-unit.source: Therefore, to set up the binding you only have to set the <xref:System.Windows.Data.Binding.Path%2A?displayProperty=fullName>.
trans-unit.target: Portanto, para configurar a associação você só precisa definir <xref:System.Windows.Data.Binding.Path%2A?displayProperty=fullName>.</xref:System.Windows.Data.Binding.Path%2A?displayProperty=fullName>

trans-unit.source: Optionally, you can specify a <xref:System.Windows.Data.Binding.Converter%2A?displayProperty=fullName> if your data source and target are different types.
trans-unit.target: Opcionalmente, você pode especificar um <xref:System.Windows.Data.Binding.Converter%2A?displayProperty=fullName>se sua fonte de dados e de destino forem de tipos diferentes.</xref:System.Windows.Data.Binding.Converter%2A?displayProperty=fullName>

trans-unit.source: For more information about data binding, see [Data Binding (WPF)](~/add/includes/ajax-current-ext-md.md).
trans-unit.target: Para obter mais informações sobre associação de dados, consulte [associação de dados (WPF)](~/add/includes/ajax-current-ext-md.md).

trans-unit.source: You can customize the DataGridCheckBoxColumn by setting properties, such as <xref:System.Windows.Controls.DataGridColumn.Width%2A>, <xref:System.Windows.Controls.DataGridColumn.Header%2A>, <xref:System.Windows.Controls.DataGridCheckBoxColumn.IsThreeState%2A>, and <xref:System.Windows.Controls.DataGridColumn.IsReadOnly%2A>.
trans-unit.target: Você pode personalizar o DataGridCheckBoxColumn definindo propriedades, como <xref:System.Windows.Controls.DataGridColumn.Width%2A>, <xref:System.Windows.Controls.DataGridColumn.Header%2A>, <xref:System.Windows.Controls.DataGridCheckBoxColumn.IsThreeState%2A>e <xref:System.Windows.Controls.DataGridColumn.IsReadOnly%2A>.</xref:System.Windows.Controls.DataGridColumn.IsReadOnly%2A> </xref:System.Windows.Controls.DataGridCheckBoxColumn.IsThreeState%2A> </xref:System.Windows.Controls.DataGridColumn.Header%2A> </xref:System.Windows.Controls.DataGridColumn.Width%2A>

trans-unit.source: If you want to display other types of data, <xref:System.Windows.Controls.DataGrid> provides the following column types: |Column Type|Data Display| |-----------------|------------------| |<xref:System.Windows.Controls.DataGridHyperlinkColumn>|Use to display URI data.| |<xref:System.Windows.Controls.DataGridComboBoxColumn>|Use to display enumeration data.| |<xref:System.Windows.Controls.DataGridTextColumn>|Use to display text.| If you want to use other controls in your <xref:System.Windows.Controls.DataGrid>, you can create your own column types by using <xref:System.Windows.Controls.DataGridTemplateColumn>.
trans-unit.target: Se você quiser exibir outros tipos de dados, <xref:System.Windows.Controls.DataGrid>fornece os seguintes tipos de coluna: | Tipo de coluna | Exibição de dados | |-----------------|------------------| | <xref:System.Windows.Controls.DataGridHyperlinkColumn>| Use para exibir dados URI. | | <xref:System.Windows.Controls.DataGridComboBoxColumn>| Use para exibir dados de enumeração. | | <xref:System.Windows.Controls.DataGridTextColumn>| Use para exibir texto. | Se você deseja usar outros controles em seu <xref:System.Windows.Controls.DataGrid>você pode criar seus próprios tipos de coluna usando <xref:System.Windows.Controls.DataGridTemplateColumn>.</xref:System.Windows.Controls.DataGridTemplateColumn> </xref:System.Windows.Controls.DataGrid> </xref:System.Windows.Controls.DataGridTextColumn> </xref:System.Windows.Controls.DataGridComboBoxColumn> </xref:System.Windows.Controls.DataGridHyperlinkColumn> </xref:System.Windows.Controls.DataGrid>

trans-unit.source: Gets or sets a value that indicates whether the hosted <xref href="System.Windows.Controls.CheckBox"></xref> controls enable three states or two.
trans-unit.target: Obtém ou define um valor que indica se o hospedado <xref href="System.Windows.Controls.CheckBox"> </xref> controles permitem três estados ou dois.

trans-unit.source: The IsThreeState property lets you use a nullable Boolean as the data type and has the same functionality as the <xref:System.Windows.Controls.Primitives.ToggleButton.IsThreeState%2A?displayProperty=fullName> property on <xref:System.Windows.Controls.CheckBox>.
trans-unit.target: A propriedade IsThreeState lhe permite usar um booliano que permite valor nulo como tipo de dados e tem a mesma funcionalidade que a <xref:System.Windows.Controls.Primitives.ToggleButton.IsThreeState%2A?displayProperty=fullName>propriedade <xref:System.Windows.Controls.CheckBox>.</xref:System.Windows.Controls.CheckBox> </xref:System.Windows.Controls.Primitives.ToggleButton.IsThreeState%2A?displayProperty=fullName>

trans-unit.source: The three states for the <xref:System.Windows.Controls.Primitives.ToggleButton.IsChecked%2A?displayProperty=fullName> property of the <xref:System.Windows.Controls.CheckBox> control are `true`, `false`, and `null`.
trans-unit.target: Os três estados para o <xref:System.Windows.Controls.Primitives.ToggleButton.IsChecked%2A?displayProperty=fullName>propriedade o <xref:System.Windows.Controls.CheckBox>controle são `true`, `false`, e `null`.</xref:System.Windows.Controls.CheckBox> </xref:System.Windows.Controls.Primitives.ToggleButton.IsChecked%2A?displayProperty=fullName>

trans-unit.target: <xref uid="langword_csharp_true" name="true" href=""></xref>Se os controles hospedados oferecer suporte a três estados; <xref uid="langword_csharp_false" name="false" href=""> </xref> se eles oferecem suporte a dois estados.

trans-unit.source: Called when a cell in the column enters editing mode.
trans-unit.target: Chamado quando uma célula na coluna entra em modo de edição.

trans-unit.source: The <xref:System.Windows.Controls.DataGrid> control calls the <xref:System.Windows.Controls.DataGridColumn.PrepareCellForEdit%2A> method when a cell in a column derived from <xref:System.Windows.Controls.DataGridColumn> enters editing mode.
trans-unit.target: O <xref:System.Windows.Controls.DataGrid>controlar chamadas de <xref:System.Windows.Controls.DataGridColumn.PrepareCellForEdit%2A>método quando uma célula em uma coluna derivada de <xref:System.Windows.Controls.DataGridColumn>entra em modo de edição.</xref:System.Windows.Controls.DataGridColumn> </xref:System.Windows.Controls.DataGridColumn.PrepareCellForEdit%2A> </xref:System.Windows.Controls.DataGrid>

trans-unit.source: The <xref:System.Windows.Controls.DataGridCheckBoxColumn> class overrides this method to respond immediately to the user gesture by updating the value in the hosted <xref:System.Windows.Controls.CheckBox> control.
trans-unit.target: O <xref:System.Windows.Controls.DataGridCheckBoxColumn>classe substitui esse método para responder imediatamente para o gesto do usuário atualizando o valor em hospedado <xref:System.Windows.Controls.CheckBox>controle.</xref:System.Windows.Controls.CheckBox> </xref:System.Windows.Controls.DataGridCheckBoxColumn>

trans-unit.source: This immediate response is necessary because a <xref:System.Windows.Controls.DataGridCheckBoxColumn> cell enters edit mode with the same user gesture that changes the state of its hosted <xref:System.Windows.Controls.CheckBox>.
trans-unit.target: Essa resposta imediata é necessária porque uma <xref:System.Windows.Controls.DataGridCheckBoxColumn>célula entra em modo de edição com o mesmo gesto do usuário que altera o estado de seu <xref:System.Windows.Controls.CheckBox>.</xref:System.Windows.Controls.CheckBox> hospedado</xref:System.Windows.Controls.DataGridCheckBoxColumn>

trans-unit.target: Informações sobre o gesto do usuário que está causando uma célula para entrar no modo de edição.

trans-unit.target: O valor não editado.
